snippet.title: The Awakening of Mummies (Nintendo Switch™)
snippet.description:
Available on Nintendo Switch:
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/the-awakening-of-mummies-switch/

////***////***////

Using your puzzle-solving skills, guide all mummies through various chambers full of traps to finally set them free from the evil Pharaoh Cléo.

////***////***////

The Awakening of Mummies

Developed by Virtual Arts Studio
Published by Silesia Games

Release date:  November 17, 2022

////***////***////
